content.name: Kingston Microsd 128gb Canvas Go! Plus
content.description: Plus UHS-I microSDXC Memory Card from Kingston features a storage capacity of 128GB and takes advantage of the UHS-I bus to support read speeds of up to 170 MB/s and write speeds of up to 90 MB/s. Plus card supports the V30 speed class which guarantees minimum write speeds of 30 MB/s. If your device does not support the V30 speed class this card also supports the U3 speed class which likewise guarantees minimum write speeds of 30 MB/s. If your device only supports the Class 10 standard minimum write speeds are guaranteed not to drop below 10 MB/s. Aside from support for UHS-I V30 and U3 Kingston also built this card with support for the Application Performance Class 2 (A2) spec which includes optimizations to give Android users an improved mobile experience delivering faster mobile app performance. The A2 spec allows the card to manage random read input-output access per second (IOPS) operations so it can quickly open apps and process accompanying tasks such as audio graphics saved profiles and in-app permissions. Built and tested to withstand harsh environments Kingston's 128GB Canvas Go! Plus UHS-I microSDXC Memory Card is protected against water shock vibration x-rays and temperature extremes. Additionally included is a microSD to SD adapter with a write protect switch allowing this card to be used in SD-compatible devices.

Cerametallic -subwoofer är exceptionellt lätt och mycket stadig. Den producerar ett anmärkningsvärt lågt frekvensområde med mycket låg distorsion och en renare uteffekt med lägre förstärkareffekt. RCA-ingångar och en trådlös WA-ingång kan användas för att ansluta subwoofern till två olika ljudsystem. Du kan till exempel använda den trådlösa ingången för ditt hemmabiosystem och RCA-ingången för ditt 2-kanalsystem utan att behöva ändra anslutning när du byter ljudkälla. Ingångar: L/R line-nivå/LFE RCA Trådlös WA-2

content.name: Klipsch The Fives
content.description: Prisbelönt akustik, den senaste generationens DSP och tuning i kombination med subtila vänster och höger kanaler har fibern avtagbart magnetgaller, flera ytbehandlingsalternativ och en subwooferutgång. Fivorna är de mest mångsidiga högtalarna på jorden. Med de användarvänliga högupplösta högtalarna som är anslutna direkt till din TV kan du avsevärt förbättra ljudet på din TV. Fives har den prisbelönta patenterade Klipsch reference akustisk teknik med laddad hup. Integrerad dynamisk ekvalisering säkerställer kraftfull bas vid alla volymer. Fives har också 192 kHz/24-bitars dekodering för perfekt uppspelning av högupplösta ljudspår. Fives är de första strömförsörjda bildskärmarna på marknaden med HDMI-ARC som är anslutna direkt till en TV för att få ett diskret, högupplöst 2-kanalsljud. De innehåller en förförstärkare, Bluetooth 5, HDMI-ARC, digitala optiska ingångar, analoga Cinch- och USB-ingångar och en subwooferutgång. Handgjorda med äkta träfinish och högkvalitativa metallkontroller.

content.name: Arozzi Arena Gaming Desk Svart
content.description: Instruktionsvideo på hur man bygger färdigt Arozzi gamingbord br Gaming takes center stage in Arozzi's Arena–the all new gaming desk. Arena is a completely new design, developed by our Swedish design team with gamers to maximize play and comfort. The 160cm (5’ 3”) width allows for three large monitors to envelop you in the game environment. The 82 cm (2’ 8¼”) depth gives you a huge field of play for your mouse, keyboard or other devices. And it all fits cleanly thanks to Arena’s unique cable management scheme. Arena’s use of high density, solid construction materials means that gamers will have a stable, placid surface to work with allowing for lightning fast responses and comfort. The customized mouse pad covers 100% of the surface and adheres tightly to the desktop with special materials. The substantial all-metal base supports it all firmly and is user adjustable for height, further enhancing comfort. The Arena has a myriad of other features which show the careful attention to detail of Arozzi’s Swedish design team and their immersion into the needs of gamers around the world. Those features include the design of the custom mouse pad which has a microfiber cloth surface which is water-resistant and machine washable. The mousepad’s edges are stitched and the pad is 5 mm thick to maximize user comfort. Finally, the whole mousepad weighs an impressive seven pounds (3.2 kg) which together with the non-slip underside means it is impervious to any random movement over the surface.

content.name: Arozzi Verona V2 Gaming Stol - Svart
content.description: Meet Verona v2 where Arozzi takes you to the next level. Our Swedish designers have integrated the most popular features from our other product lines along with the latest in ergonomic design to produce a gaming chair that puts you at the centre of control and comfort. Supple pleather covering over a lightweight metal frame gives a luxury feel while maintaining the flexibility to move and react quickly. The Verona v2 includes ergonomic features like extra padded seating, adjustable armrests, adjustable back and head support. The durable pleather upholstery is also easy to clean. Verona v2 comes in a variety of exciting colors to enhance your space. When it's time to win the Verona v2 will get you across the line with comfort to spare. Improved Features 1,5 cm wider metalframe. Thicker and more durable Pleather upholstery. Adjustable recline angle up to 160°. Nylon composite, heavy duty base. Features Ergonomic design High density shaped foam in the seat for excellent comfort. Adjustable armrests (Height) Rocking function Metal frame A durable metal frame structure ensures stability and durability. Class-4 gas lift Durable for up to 140kg!
